
* Activate the virtual environment:

cd /home/nimthara/Desktop/galaxy
source .venv/bin/activate

* Check which Python the terminal is using

which python

  should print: /home/nimthara/Desktop/galaxy/.venv/bin/python

* Run the script again:

python fit_emission_lines.py

* Changing  sky position and radius
python fit_emission_lines.py --position "12h30m00s +20d00m00s" --radius 3.0
